Face: Cougar skin mask quest <br>
If your higher lvl buddy can free up some time and take you to iceclad w/ 2 mammoth meats (from anywhere) and I believe 2 med qual cougar skins you can get a the mask by turning them in to quest giver (see Allakhazams Magical realm for more details) ac6 +2 dex / agi +10 hp<br>
Finger: Jagged Bands +5 ac +3 str go to ec they go for 20-30 p a piece <br>
Hands: Dark mail guantlets +10 ac +5 dex +50 mana <br>
 bought mine for 100p in my early 20's used them until late 30's when i bought my Gauntlets of the Black<br>
Chest: Dusty Bp +22 ac +5 sta +20 hp usually go for about 200p <br>
Tattered Mantle or Crested Spaulders both usually go for a couple of hundred plat and are great upgrades you could keep for a very long time.<br>
Some things to go for in your 30's:<br>
Hero bracer +9 ac +10 str +5 sv poi/dis - quested<br>
Save up for Gauntlets of the Black +15 ac +4 str +3 wis<br>
Ro greaves - quested or save up for Crustacean Shell legs the dex hit (-4) is kind of big but the +16 sta more than makes up for it.<br>
Feet: save up for crustacean shell boots instead of Ro they are lower ac but the Sta makes up for the hp diff and ac diff IMOHP.  Not to mention both pieces have str stat as well.  <br>
Also save up for Ry'gorr neckguard / fire opal wedding bands (ac / hp rings - crafted and a bit costly)<br>
and DW gear.  <br>
